OL,3,CReview into police contact with mother
OL,4,Cwho killed two children
OL,6,FA review into how police initially
OL,7,Fdealt with a mother who went on to
OL,8,Fkill her two children has been
OL,9,Fordered, after the response was
OL,10,Fbranded 'unacceptable'.
OL,12,FVeronique John was arrested in June
OL,13,Fafter she attacked her husband, Nathan
OL,14,FJohn, with a piece of wood at their
OL,15,Fhome in Stoke.
OL,17,FJohn, 50, was handed a community
OL,18,Fresolution notice and allowed to
OL,19,Freturn to the family's address on Flax
OL,20,FStreet the day after.
