OL,4,Cwho killed two children
OL,6,FJust hours later she killed her two
OL,7,Fchildren Ethan and Elizabeth John at
OL,8,Ftheir home - and tried to kill Nathan
OL,9,Fat a nearby Campbell Road car wash.
OL,11,FEarlier this month she was handed an
OL,12,Findefinite hospital order for the
OL,13,Fdouble murder of her two children
OL,14,Fafter she was deemed unfit to stand
OL,15,Ftrial.
OL,17,FEthan 8, had been stabbed more than 20
OL,18,Ftimes and Elizabeth, 7, had brain
OL,19,Fdamage from the attack.
