OL,6,FStaffordshire Police has now branded
OL,7,Fits own response into the handling of
OL,8,FVeronique John's initial arrest as
OL,9,F'unacceptable' - and the case is
OL,10,Fcurrently being reviewed by the
OL,11,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,12,F(IOPC).
