OL,3,CReview into police contact with mother
OL,4,Cwho killed two children
OL,6,FA Staffordshire Police spokesman said:
OL,7,F"On Saturday 10 June 2023, Veronique
OL,8,FJohn was arrested on suspicion of
OL,9,Fassault. The victim did not wish to
OL,10,Fprovide a statement or make a
OL,11,Fcomplaint. After being questioned in
OL,12,Fcustody, she was given a restorative
OL,13,Fdisposal and released the following
OL,14,Fday.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
