OL,3,CReview into police contact with mother
OL,4,Cwho killed two children
OL,6,F"We made a mandatory referral to the
OL,7,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,8,Fon 12 June 2023 due to recent police
OL,9,Fcontact with Veronique John. On 16
OL,10,FJune 2023, the IOPC directed that a
OL,11,Flocal investigation should take place
OL,12,Finto the previous police contact.
OL,14,F"Our Professional Standards Department
OL,15,Fcompleted their investigation which
OL,16,Ffound the service level provided was
OL,17,Funacceptable. As is standard in these
OL,18,Fcircumstances, we sent a report back
OL,19,Ffor the IOPC to review which is
OL,20,Fcurrently being considered."
