OL,3,CReview into police contact with mother
OL,4,Cwho killed two children
OL,6,FAn IOPC spokesman said: "A mandatory
OL,7,Freferral was made to us by
OL,8,FStaffordshire Police on 12 June last
OL,9,Fyear due to their previous contact
OL,10,Fwith Veronique John. The information
OL,11,Fprovided to us indicated that when
OL,12,Fdisclosures were made to police, any
OL,13,Fthreat appeared to be directed towards
OL,14,Fher husband rather than the children.
OL,15,FFrom the detail given, it was not
OL,16,Fclear that police would have been
OL,17,Faware that there was a real and
OL,18,Fimmediate risk to the children.
