OL,3,CReview into police contact with mother
OL,4,Cwho killed two children
OL,6,F"After careful assessment, we decided
OL,7,Fan investigation was required but that
OL,8,Fit was suitable for the force to carry
OL,9,Fout and that a sufficient level of
OL,10,Foversight would be provided by the
OL,11,Fforce sending the IOPC their report if
OL,12,Fno conduct was identified.
OL,13,FStaffordshire Police have now sent us
OL,14,Ftheir investigation report, which we
OL,15,Fare currently reviewing. Our
OL,16,Fsympathies are with all those affected
OL,17,Fby this tragedy."
